  <original-body>Many times I found my self needing to increment a lot of counters at the same time, but it's not possible yet.

Now we can do:

Model.increment_counter :points, [1, 2, 3]
Model.decrement_counter :points, [1, 2, 3]
Model.update_counters [1, 2, 3], :points =&gt; 1</original-body>
